From: Monk Liu <Monk.Liu@amd.com>
Date: Tue, 26 Nov 2019 19:38:22 +0800
Subject: drm/amdgpu: do autoload right after MEC loaded for SRIOV VF
Git-commit: dacf56e45ded829a87cefab17bf6800d6cacd236
Patch-mainline: v5.5-rc1
References: bsc#1152489

since we don't have RLCG ucode loading and no SRlist as well

Signed-off-by: Monk Liu <Monk.Liu@amd.com>
Reviewed-by: Hawking Zhang <Hawking.Zhang@amd.com>
Signed-off-by: Alex Deucher <alexander.deucher@amd.com>
Acked-by: Thomas Zimmermann <tzimmermann@suse.de>
---
 drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/amdgpu_psp.c | 4 ++--
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)

diff --git a/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/amdgpu_psp.c b/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/amdgpu_psp.c
index 2770cba56a6b..44be3a45b25e 100644
--- a/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/amdgpu_psp.c
+++ b/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/amdgpu_psp.c
@@ -1487,8 +1487,8 @@ static int psp_np_fw_load(struct psp_context *psp)
 			return ret;
 
 		/* Start rlc autoload after psp recieved all the gfx firmware */
-		if (psp->autoload_supported && ucode->ucode_id ==
-			AMDGPU_UCODE_ID_RLC_RESTORE_LIST_SRM_MEM) {
+		if (psp->autoload_supported && ucode->ucode_id == (amdgpu_sriov_vf(adev) ?
+		    AMDGPU_UCODE_ID_CP_MEC2 : AMDGPU_UCODE_ID_RLC_RESTORE_LIST_SRM_MEM)) {
 			ret = psp_rlc_autoload(psp);
 			if (ret) {
 				DRM_ERROR("Failed to start rlc autoload\n");
